<P>This was al ju$t&mdash;for any thing the company knew to the $Word$ certain it was, that he had been a private in a $Word$ $Word$; but, re&s;pecting the manner in which be $Word$ be had made a $Word$ mi&s;take&mdash;perhaps, his me|mory was $Word$&mdash;perhaps, he wi&s;hed to keep his own &s;e|cret&mdash;$Word$ perhaps, had told this &s;tory &s;o often, that he him&s;elf $Word$ to be per&s;uaded of it's verity. Render, he was $Word$ $ut! "For what?" a&s;ked th$$. Peace, $Word$ &s;pirit of Curio$ity! &s;eek not to bring to light the mi&s;teers of my brother, which Time has kindly left
