to fortify. He differed, he &s;aid, f$$m the received <HI>pru|dential</HI> opinion&mdash;"Many fir&s;t, and love will come after;" but advi&s;ed them, for the rea&s;ons he $a$ given, to attempt a courteous mode of $Span$ towards $Word$ other, which time might upon, into $Span$. If, and $$peated $$$als, however, they &s;hould find the $Word$ &s;hall painful, on being again applied to, he prom$$$$ to take proper &s;teps for their deliverance. They m$d$ their ob$$&s;ance, and withdrew, &s;eemingly very w$ll &s;ati$fied.</P>
